    owl:unionOf ( <https://w3id.org/lmodel/mcp/TaskStatusEnum#cancelled> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/mcp/TaskStatusEnum#completed> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/mcp/TaskStatusEnum#failed> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/mcp/TaskStatusEnum#input_required> <https://w3id.org/lmodel/mcp/TaskStatusEnum#working> ) ;
